Key features :
‎
‎Tracking the supply chain from field to port
‎
‎Real-time dashboard for each player (producer, cooperative, customs, buyer)
‎
‎Blockchain archiving of certificates, documents and inspections
‎
‎Automatic alerts on anomalies (AI)
‎
‎Integration of certification standards (BIO, UTZ, Rainforest)
‎
‎Smart contracts between producers, buyers and transporters
‎
‎Impact :
‎
‎Significant reduction in fraud and disputes
‎
‎End-to-end transparency
‎
‎Greater negotiating power for producers
‎
‎Reduced losses and administrative errors
‎
‎Easier access to financing thanks to verifiable data flows
‎
